   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Rebuild Puerto Rico through Glass Recycling</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Puerto Rico is an island in the Caribbean sea and is one of the most biodiverse territories of the United States. Currently, Puerto Rico lacks an efficient solid waste management system that promotes recycling. For this reason, materials like glass end up polluting the soil and the sea. Our project will support the value chain of glass with recycling initiatives and using the material gathered as raw materials for local companies to create sustainable construction materials and rebuild Puerto.</narrative>
  </description>
